==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: The eighteen changes of a grown woman.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: nǚ dà shí bā biàn

===Idiom===
'''[[女]][[大]][[十]][[八]][[变]]'''

# All of the changes that a girl makes when turning into a woman.

#: ''[[小时候]]，[[徐]][[妈妈]][[对]][[自己]][[这个]][[难看]][[的]][[小]][[女儿]][[十分]][[失望]]。[[但是]]，'''女大十八变'''，[[小S]][[如今]][[已经]][[成为]][[亭亭玉立]][[的]][[小]][[天鹅]]。'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

===Alternate forms===
[[女大十八變]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

